{"title":"「长乐国庆集训2018ROUND3」2.国家","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5166#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/submissions?problem_id=5166","statistics":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5166/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5166/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/discussion/problem/5166"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"给定正整数$n,p$和非负整数$a,b$，求 ，例如当$n=1$时，该结果等于$a+b$。由于答案可能很大，请对$p$取模。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"多组数据。\r\n\n\r\n\n第一行，一个正整数$T$，表示数据组数。\r\n\n\r\n\n接下来$T$行，每行四个整数$n,a,b,p$，表示一组数据，相邻两个数之间有空格隔开。\r\n\n"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"共$T$行，每行一个非负整数，表示一组数据的答案。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"【样例输入】\r\n```\r\n3\r\n2 3 3 233\r\n5 1 2 100\r\n1000 233 666 998244353\r\n```\r\n【样例输出】\r\n```\r\n27\r\n63\r\n952904376\r\n``` \r\n另一组见附加文件（如果有）"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于30%的数据，满足$T \\le 10$，$n,a,b \\le 10^6$，$p=10^9+7$。\r\n\n\r\n\n对于60%的数据，满足$T \\le 10,000$，$n,a,b \\le 10^9$，$p=10^9+7$。\r\n\n\r\n\n另有10%的数据，满足$a=0$。\r\n\n\r\n\n另有10%的数据，满足$a=1$。\r\n\n\r\n\n对于100%的数据，满足$T \\le 30,000$，$n,a,b,p \\le 10^{12}$。\r\n\n"}]}